sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant DesignModule as Database Design Module
    participant Backend
    participant Database

    User->>Frontend: Open database design screen
    activate Frontend
    Frontend->>DesignModule: Initialize design workspace
    activate DesignModule
    DesignModule->>Backend: Request existing schemas
    activate Backend
    Backend->>Database: Fetch schemas
    activate Database
    Database-->>Backend: Schemas
    deactivate Database
    Backend-->>DesignModule: Schemas data
    deactivate Backend
    DesignModule-->>Frontend: Render schemas
    deactivate DesignModule

    User->>Frontend: Create/modify tables and relations
    Frontend->>DesignModule: Update design model
    activate DesignModule
    DesignModule->>Backend: Validate and save design
    activate Backend
    Backend->>Database: Persist design changes
    activate Database
    Database-->>Backend: Save confirmation
    deactivate Database
    Backend-->>DesignModule: Validation result
    deactivate Backend
    DesignModule-->>Frontend: Update UI with result
    deactivate DesignModule
    Frontend-->>User: Show success/errors
    deactivate Frontend